reviewText: The dvd was in a very good condition

I caught up with Shania Twain in early 1998, so I missed experiencing this early phenomenal part of her career. Although the first song I heard was From This Moment On, I am well aware of the success of The Woman In ME CD.

I am a huge and dedicated fan of this lady. She has it all, a talented songwriter, amazing performer who can mesmerize an audience, not to mention she is beautiful on the inside as well as on the outside. I found this DVD to be informative, yet not going into, or expanding into more of her overall achievements. I realize the DVD keys on Any Man Of Mine, and so taking that into consideration, it is well done in my opinion. It touches briefly on a lot of her key accomplishments.

As a dedicated Shania fan, I would recommend "Impact! Songs That Changed The World: Shania Twain - Any Man of Mine" to anyone who is a dedicated fan like myself, or just for anyone who would like to know more about Shania Twain.

Steve
This 22 minute program shows the impact Shania Twain has had on female artists in country music, and country music in general over the past decade. If you are a fan defintely check it out
